// @description  Th√™m th·ªùi gian ngh·ªâ ng·∫´u nhi√™n gi·ªØa c√°c b∆∞·ªõc v√† gi·ªØa c√°c s·∫£n ph·∫©m ƒë·ªÉ gi·ªëng ng∆∞·ªùi th·∫≠t.
// @author       HaiTrinh
// @match        https://www.etsy.com/your/shops/*/tools/listings*
// @match        https://www.etsy.com/your/shops/*/listing-editor/*
